Austin decided to take a caffeine break so I got some @ryzesuperfoods to try and we really like it! 
It’s got 6 different mushrooms in it. 
🍄 Cordyceps for stamina 
🍄 Lions Mane for focus 
🍄 Reishi for stress relief 
🍄 Shitake for immunity 
🍄 Turkey tail for digestion 
🍄 Kings Trumpet for inflammation 
They also have a coconut mushroom creamer to can get to add to it. It’s been a great mid day “pick me up” 
.
.
.

Getting my hormones checked and balanced @edgeweightlossandfatigue was such a game changer for me. I should have done it a long time ago. HTR supplementing my working hard in the gym and clean eating has helped me drop 3% body fat in just 3 months and gained half a pound of muscle in the first 30 days. It’s amazing how different I feel and look in such a short amount of time. We just can’t function at our max potential when none of those things are right. Feeling really good and motivated. P.S. I love these tube socks 😋
.
.
.
